        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>IN NOMINE DOMINI SALVATORIS NOSTRI IESU CHRISTI DEI ETERNI. <persName
                            key="#Princeps #Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis" ref="#people/3010">SECUNDUS
                            RICHARDUS</persName> DIVINA ORDINANTE CLEMENTIA CAPUANORUM <rs
                            key="#Princeps">PRINCEPS</rs> PETITIONIBUS DILECTORUM SUORUM BARONUM
                        CLEMENTER A[C] CLEMENTER FAVET. IGITUR fidelium nostrorum presentium ac
                        futurorum noverit multitudo, quoniam <rs key="#Intercessory"
                            >interveniente</rs> domno <persName key="#Intercessory #Bishops"
                            ref="#people/3056">Iohanne</persName>, <placeName
                            key="#Cities #Dioecesis" ref="#places/4000">Aversane</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Dioecesis">sedis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopo</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Witness #Count #childOf" ref="#people/2422"
                            >Robberto</persName>
                        <persName key="#Count" ref="#people/4236">Rannulfi</persName>, <rs
                            key="#Count">comitis</rs>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filio</rs>, <persName ref="#people/4251"
                            key="#Intercessory">Hugo de Molinis</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Witness" ref="#people/3076">Willelmo de
                            Pirolo</persName>, <persName key="#Intercessory #Witness"
                            ref="#people/3020">Robberto de Medania</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory" ref="#people/5016">Thoma de Venabile</persName>,
                            <persName key="#Intercessory #Witness" ref="#people/3080">Raynaldo
                            Lopino</persName>, <persName key="#Intercessory" ref="#people/5017"
                            >Raynaldo de Matalone</persName>, <persName ref="#people/4253"
                            key="#Intercessory #Witness">Rannulfo, filio Guale</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Intercessory #Witness" ref="#people/5018">Radulfo de
                            Mucegros</persName>, nostris dilectis baronibus, anime nostrae et omnium
                        nostrorum saluti providens, in perpetuum concedimus et confirmamus Aversane
                            <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3053" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Pauli apostoli</orgName>
                        <rs key="#Mother_churches">aecclesiae</rs> quicquid ei a tempore <persName
                            key="#Count" ref="#people/3060">Rannulfi</persName>, primi Aversanorum
                            <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs> concessum est vel ab ipso vel a
                        successoribus suis <persName ref="#people/5019">Radulfo
                            Trincanocto</persName>, <persName key="#Princeps #grandparentOf"
                            ref="#people/3001">Richardo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principe</rs>
                        <rs key="#grandparentOf">avo</rs> et <persName key="#Princeps #parentOf"
                            ref="#people/3002">Iordano</persName>
                        <rs key="#Princeps">principe</rs>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">patre</rs> nostro, et ab omnibus eiusdem baronibus cum
                        licentia <rs key="#Count">comitum</rs> vel <rs key="#Princeps"
                            >principum</rs> vel vasvassoribus cum licentia domnorum suorum concessum
                        aut concedendum est, ita ut nullus eiusdem aecclesiae <rs key="#Bishops"
                            >episcopum</rs> aut <rs key="#Other_clerics">clericos</rs> in
                        beneficiorum subtractione quae possident vel possessuri sunt, inquietare
                        presumat. <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Churches"
                            >Aecclesias</rs> scilicet cum omnibus suis pertinentiis, <rs
                            key="#Decima">decimas</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >terras cultas vel incultas</rs> cum <rs
                            key="#Mountains #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >montibus</rs> et planitie, cum <rs
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >silvis</rs>, <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >aquis</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Fisheries #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure"
                            >piscationibus</rs>, cum omnibus inferioribus ac superioribus earum,
                        quin etiam <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">hominibus</rs> cum omnibus eorum rebus,
                        ad persolvendum predicte aecclesiae <rs key="#Public_exactions">quicquid
                            parti rei publice facere et persolvere debent aut debuerint</rs>. Haec
                        omnia predicte aecclesiae Sancti Pauli apostoli Aversanae sedis, in
                        perpetuum concedimus et confirmamus, ad possessionem et potestatem et
                        dominationem prephate aecclesiae et prephati domni Iohanni aepiscopi eiusque
                        successoribus. Remota omni inquietudine et molestatione principum
                        successorum nostrorum vel vice principum, comitum vel vice comitum, iudicum,
                        sculdahorum, castaldeorum aliorumque omnium mortalium. Quod si quis huius
                        nostrae concessionis et confirmationis pagine contemptor aut in aliquo eius
                        violator esse presumpserit, <rs key="#Penalty">quingentas libras auri
                            purissimi</rs> persolvat, medietatem nostro sacro palatio et medietatem
                        predicte aecclesiae Sancti Pauli apostoli Aversane sedis, et predicto domni
                        Iohanni episcopo eiusque successoribus. Solutaque pena librarum, haec nostra
                        concessio et confirmatio, firma, munita atque inconvulsa maneat in
                        perpetuum. Et ut hoc firmius credatur et diligentius ab omnibus observetur,
                        manu propria subscripsimus et nostri sigilli impressione iussimus insigniri.
                        SIGNUM DOMNI (M) SECUNDI RICHARDI PRINCIPIS. + EGO ROBBERTUS COMES. Ex
                        iussione prephate serenissime potestatis scripsi EGO <persName
                            key="#Writer #Judge" ref="#people/3012">QUIRIACUS</persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">IUDEX</rs> in anno dominice incarnationis M. monagesimo
                        quinto, et sexto decimo anno principatus ipsius domni secundi Richardi <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">gloriosi</rs> principis. DATUM mense
                        octubrio, per indictionem quartam. + Ego Willelmus de Pirolo. + Ego
                        Rannulfus filius Guale. + Ego Rodulfus de Mucegros. + Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness" ref="#people/3032">Aymo de Argentia</persName>. + Ego
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes de Doeli">Ihon de
                                Doeli</name></persName>. + Robbertus de Medania. + <persName
                            key="#Witness" ref="#people/4249">Ugo de Faida</persName>. + <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Bartholomaeus">Bartholomeus</name></persName>.
                        + <persName key="#Witness #Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3078"
                            >Stantio</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">vice princeps</rs>. Raynaldus Lopinus.
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Raginaldus"
                            >Raynaldus</name></persName>. </ab>
                </div>
